Body: running model dataset, latest master v3 took 25 minutes finish 1000 iterations v2 took 10 minutes. kernels first three convolutional layers 9, 7 5 pixels. problem also reported fork caffe https github.com happynear caffe windows issues 24 many sources https www.google.co.in ?gws rd ssl newwindow 1 q cudnn v3 slower . maybe cudnn v3 works well maxwell architecture gpus can't choose efficient convolution algorithm. simplest solution revert older version caffe since v2 longer supported https github.com bvlc caffe pull 3218 nvidia fix problem. still want keep caffe date experiment new features batch normalization. second way specify convolution algorithm explicitly flexible enough various model configurations. last resort keep backwards compatibility cudnn v2 caffe.

Body: please use caffe users list https groups.google.com forum !forum caffe users usage, installation, modeling questions, requests help. post requests issues. interferes development caffe. please read guidelines contributing https github.com bvlc caffe blob master contributing.md submitting issue. issue summary steps reproduce difficulty building caffe training model, please ask caffe users mailing list. reporting build error seems due bug caffe, please attach build configuration either makefile.config cmakecache.txt output make cmake command. system configuration operating system compiler cuda version applicable cudnn version applicable blas python matlab version pycaffe matcaffe respectively
